                                â€¢ Normal chance: ${bot.wagerStats.chanceNormal}%<br>
                                â€¢ Recovery chance: ${bot.wagerStats.chanceRecovery}%<br>
                                â€¢ Max chance: ${bot.wagerStats.chanceMax}% (resets to normal if exceeded)<br>
                                â€¢ Chance increases by 0.5% each bet when in recovery
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- LABOUCHERE TAB -->
                <div class="tab-content" id="tab-labouchere">
                    <div class="section">
                        <div class="section-title">ðŸŽ² Labouchere System</div>
                        
